blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 不過我指商業裝修個d 好似商店，寫字樓個d。起碼唔駛日曬雨淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cc37b54f224e22bbfaedd0761e6188d4dcad6a","tid":270942,"uid":62424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:46:32.000Z","msg":"日薪幾多先"},{"pid":"a4c959d187b7448103865a9d6f1296d49ca466a3","tid":270942,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同工種師傅人工地盤比裝修高<br />\n我個行師傅係地盤同裝修人工個差距超過四成<br />\n但當然你計接野做就唔同計法</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見電燈佬地盤同裝修個價差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4807363408b6b6a5b1c77747ead1be4bd0d41b","tid":270942,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日薪幾多先</blockquote><br />\n睇你咩工種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51496be25fbfe29eeee0052c8bd97e0330f8120","tid":270942,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:48:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9173a73e3d10530ffb1871dfcfeed8313d4074f6","tid":270942,"uid":29087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T23:52:36.000Z","msg":"點解你覺得地盤一定要曬?我唔信裝修cap水勁過地盤判頭"},{"pid":"6ddf8328d4880857b590010fbb9c34f11552bd68","tid":270942,"uid":118246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T00:56:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你覺得地盤一定要曬?我唔信裝修cap水勁過地盤判頭</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n睇你外裝定內裝姐。咁一定，規模根本唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"743ad77059e1551e2f47723152d1b972954f4e94","tid":270942,"uid":13987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:00:44.000Z","msg":"召喚高學歷裝修佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}